【Versatile and Perfect Gift】: The baby crib set are for girls and boys, can be matched to any crib toddler bed, dressing up the room, grandparents house, preschool, school, Daycare, ect. Suitable for baby napping, night sleeping, playing. Also a good gift for new parents, birthdays, baby showers, baby gender reveal parties, Halloween, Christmas, New Year's parties.

【Easy Care】: When washing for the first time, recommend machine wash or hand wash with feebly washed the water , temperature is below 30 degrees, strong detergents are forbidden, do not dry clean, iron at medium temperature, hang to dry. Cleaning according to the correct washing instructions will help protect the product and prolong its service life.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Crib Bedding Set
reviews.reviewText: This is a cute toddler bed set. I really like the microfiber texture. It is so warm and soft. Everything fit to the mattress perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This bedding set for a crib is pretty basic but nice. The packaging is unexciting but standard, just a clear plastic bag. It comes with the fitted mattress cover, a duvet cover (with corner ties) and a pillowcase. The dinosaur design is colorful and fun. Seems like good quality and it looks nice, fun set that is a good value for a kid.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute print and nice light quality
reviews.reviewText: This crib bedding set is a cute, affordable option for a toddler bed. The print is really adorable and has nice bright colors on it. The material itself is pretty thin overall, so this would be nice for a spring or summer set I think. I think it's a great value for a 3 piece set.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Anyone who has a had a pregnancy loss appreciates the meaning of the rainbow. It's called a rainbow baby symbolizing a calm after the storm. I got this because this is cute and will match baby's room. You can tell it's machine made not like a quality quilt, but the material is decent and will do for decorative purposes. One should also keep in mind that infants should not be placed with any other bedding other than a fitted sheet. So the cover and pillow case are just for fun or later use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is nice and light weight. The cover is a duvet cover but I use it as a sheet and it works perfect. Vibrant color and good quality stitching!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So pleased with this set!
reviews.reviewText: This set is SO pretty! Even nicer than in the pictures. It came with an extra pillow case too that was a surprise gift. I love the diaper bag. The pinks are a soft pink and the opposite side star pattern is cheerful. The whole set is just perfect. I definitely recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Wish pillow cases were reg size
reviews.reviewText: Pillow cases are very tiny, the blankets also pretty tiny and thin so you’ll have to use a main blanket under. Good enough to not return but not good enough to purchase again

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This set is super cute. The sheet, pillowcase and duvet are all 100% dinos. There is no turquoise on this set aside from the colors on the pattern. It's still really cute. Keep in mind it's a duvet cover and if you don't have a toddler sized duvet, the cover will be more like a double layered sheet.
